Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不動總司令他…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.65,0:00:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他留下了一張字條
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎今天一早就離開了學校
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.62,0:00:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去尋找傳說中的神話型Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.49,0:00:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有什麼線索了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.36,0:00:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.89,0:00:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創聖之書裡或許有所記載
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.32,0:00:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創聖之書
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.16,0:00:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有這麼多洞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.03,0:00:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.28,0:00:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個還真是夠深的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.48,0:00:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安迪同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.52,0:00:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.72,0:01:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這之前還超活躍的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.54,0:01:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 安迪挖出來的溫泉真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.01,0:01:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.86,0:01:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼頭緒嗎 Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.13,0:01:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.34,0:01:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底是怎麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.99,0:01:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.37,0:01:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,================OP===============
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.11,0:01:33.67,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絶望的に君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.82,0:01:40.87,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反転する世界のプラトニック 愛し合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.11,0:01:56.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らが見てる世界は いつでも逆さまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:02:06.99,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうしようもないことで たいがい決まってく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:19.07,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙するほど傷つく瞳 心で叫びながら黙っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:29.66,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後のふたり 混ざれないまま 秒読みが聞こえてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:35.82,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絶望的に君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:41.67,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すたれゆく動物みたいに愛し合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.73,0:02:46.04,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泣きたいくらい君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:49.38,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反転する世界のプラトニック
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:52.39,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感じたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.11,0:01:33.67,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你美得令人絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.82,0:01:40.87,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們在倒錯的精神世界中相愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.11,0:01:56.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們眼裡的世界總是相互顛倒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:02:06.99,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幾乎要被認定為是無可奈何的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:19.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷口淌淚的眼眸 在內心沉默地叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:29.66,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的兩人來不及結合便聽到離別的倒數
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:35.82,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你美得令人絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:41.67,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們像漸趨衰老的動物一樣相愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.73,0:02:46.04,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你美得令人落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:49.38,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在倒錯的精神世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:52.39,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想細細體會…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,================OP===============
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:02:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rare·Igler
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音樂會?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 我考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要只是考慮 真的陪我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你答覆 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是約會的邀請嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變形象之後變得備受歡迎了啊 婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再甜一點就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在模擬戰時的大膽告白可能也起到了作用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給人以爽朗大方的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 是不是因為我之前說了些多餘的話你才…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是 只是想說就說罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少比之前也有所進展了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這前方又是死巷子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.82,0:03:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴白同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.12,0:03:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:03:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正要送信到宿舍樓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這封是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的 其實這也沒什麼好隱瞞的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸寄來了一封信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的父親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他相處得不怎麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.08,0:04:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以真沒想到能收到他的信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是會關心我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 畢竟是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話由我來說會不會很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽的事我還記得一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但父親的事我就完全不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 我也還有很多事情弄不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於那時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:04:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候我袒護他的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 不要開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:05:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請原諒這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不是想責怪御子乃你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為現在是大家必須齊心協力的關鍵時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的使命是讓大家團結一心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我真的不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.62,0:05:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少見啊 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.51,0:05:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的信錯寄給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 沒看清楚就拆開了封口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為老爸的字太難認了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.97,0:06:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說 這年頭不用寄信也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 那信件就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.03,0:06:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看下去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不知道為什麼Neo DEAVA要接納御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我在擔心她是否會成為你的負擔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟這女兒從小做就什麼事都做不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你希望的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.61,0:06:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以將她從Neo DEAVA帶回來然後安置在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.18,0:06:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對爸爸來說 我還是一如既往地一事無成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很擔心安迪?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:06:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在非常消沉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.93,0:07:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你們兩個一直都很要好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前遠足的時候 發生了點事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒出息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.67,0:07:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂得叫別人好好說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.48,0:07:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一輪到自己卻沒有跨出那一步的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總會不禁地把其他男人看成跟我父親一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽說過我討厭男人的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.16,0:07:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和父親相處得好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖泥帶水的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺我一直在對父親察言觀色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.94,0:07:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有話想說 也因為害怕被訓斥而一直說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是又被責罵不夠爽快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.26,0:08:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是父親 也終歸是異性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人的想法只有男人自己知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說修修是公的還是母的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訓練到這麼晚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起自己是一個女戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然最近有點莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不希望連這一長處也失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 晚安了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.20,0:09:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死巷子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運作率一片低迷 已經低破40%
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大的問題是次元轉移所耗能量過多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果繼續前往Vega
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.65,0:09:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至會影響到市民最低限度的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計屆時會引發大規模的暴動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了山窮水盡的地步了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.78,0:09:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到神樂的下落了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬分抱歉 他依然下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.14,0:09:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕又是未影從中穿針引線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人從未考慮過Altair的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好Afra Gnis的出擊準備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.74,0:10:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是要…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我親自前往Vega
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是時候要感受一下久違的戰場之上的氛圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.99,0:10:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.97,0:10:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓這世界再度響起嬰兒的啼哭聲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.10,0:10:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要找到真實的夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定還能遇到被你留在Vega的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.16,0:10:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.74,0:10:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸寄來的信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.58,0:10:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:10:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是要責怪你讀信的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是看你很失落的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.17,0:11:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 為什麼當父母的總愛瞎操心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我成為了怪炎和大家的負擔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.55,0:11:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一事無成的我還不如老老實實待在家裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從小就對人過分地察言觀色了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想觸怒或傷害對方 因而害怕說出自己的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.77,0:11:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其實你最害怕的是自己受到傷害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一直認為你是一事無成的膽小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 有個人在和我初次見面的時候就這麼說道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我跟她相識不久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我覺得現在的御子乃並不是你所說的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信御子乃也一定希望在今後能有所改變
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔他說過這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不爽 但正如他所說 你的確變了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.27,0:12:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想讓老爸也看看現在的你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首次聽到這樣的音色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉穩而高貴的聲響
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.69,0:12:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大海嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人懷念的蔚藍（青澀）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.95,0:12:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那青春的Vega
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出雲 事到如今你終於要大展宏圖了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說 你是去尋找花朵所留下的種子的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不曾見過的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充斥著敵人老大的派頭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太慢了 安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒什麼大不了的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這種地方也要挖洞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.68,0:13:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 現在的他不能派上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠出擊的Vector有五機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.73,0:13:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用兩架Vector來支援Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出擊的Element是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交由你決定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪炎 阿馬塔 還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:14:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 不能讓你們出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被禁止戰鬥的話 我將不再是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想作為一名戰士 超越作為女人的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想為大家出一份力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.22,0:14:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她們去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓男生們持續作戰也確實是有極限的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不動 我的決定沒有錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 AQUARION由阿馬塔 婕希卡和諸井搭乘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪炎和MIX從旁支援
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.29,0:14:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婕希卡那傢伙異常地焦急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此才令人分外擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總有種很不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合體吧 機首是我 沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.46,0:14:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心碎合體 GO AQUARION
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少在戰鬥的時候能在阿馬塔身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.91,0:15:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是婕希卡的情感嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.56,0:15:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然合體什麼的最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.04,0:15:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AQUARION GEPART
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.49,0:15:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,量產機就交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要因為是Vector就把我們看扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.81,0:15:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一擊定勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太青澀了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我很欣賞你那氣勢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直完全無效
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:15:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告損害情況
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西區綜合體育館一帶遭到破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.14,0:16:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人將GEPART的光線吸收後成倍奉還了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Altair已經看不到這般年少輕狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但光憑那樣是贏不了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.87,0:16:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要衝動 婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮擊戰風險太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.08,0:16:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是進行格鬥戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不用你說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸井 借你的力量給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脆弱力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超捻轉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:16:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.74,0:17:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脆弱力還真是有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不論在哪個時代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脆弱的都是年輕的那一方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了避免無意義的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓你們見識一下絕對的戰力差距吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超捻轉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同一招對我不起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.22,0:17:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GEPART被…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把合體解除了?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸井因剛才的衝擊失去了意識
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.90,0:17:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Y現正自動航行中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Element替換 御子乃出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪炎和阿馬塔、御子乃合體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婕希卡從旁支援
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.51,0:17:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的你欠缺冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.12,0:17:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼那麼急躁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.40,0:18:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔 怪炎 我們合體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.63,0:18:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人正向這邊靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺Abductor的行動不是以攻擊為目的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人侵入了我們的通信線路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.85,0:18:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vega的諸位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.15,0:18:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Altair的最高領導人出雲?神呂木
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你們的指揮官進行交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說最高領導人?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫克蕾雅·多露西娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是Neo Deava的指揮官
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.56,0:18:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指揮官也是Igler…是女性嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女性不是大多都不喜歡爭鬥的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實可以這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在一定情況和場合下 女性反而更為強悍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.33,0:18:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為某些緣故我們需要最強的Rare·Igler
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最強的Rare·Igler
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想給此地帶來災害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.82,0:19:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能將Rare·Igler接到我們的世界去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.35,0:19:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們怎麼能答應你這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.65,0:19:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且慢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.96,0:19:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理事長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果雙方有開啟談判的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不動在這裡的話他會怎樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婕希卡的Vector正在向Abductor移動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你們需要女人 我就跟你們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來就能改變現狀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.69,0:19:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架機體…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rare·Igler反應!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:19:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婕希卡 你別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.27,0:20:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多加珍惜自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.41,0:20:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的你只是在自暴自棄而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.73,0:20:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看出那個Rare·Igler有投降的意願
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕獲她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾隨合體 GO AQUARION
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AQUARION EVOL
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛翔的機械天使
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在操縱它的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認一下如何 出雲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.81,0:20:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的雙眼好好確認
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會出現這種幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔的心之弦正在被什麼人撥弄著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澈、甘甜而苦澀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.19,0:21:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是未影的把戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.89,0:21:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愛耍小聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但機械天使確實停止了行動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有錯的 那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.87,0:21:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔 大敵當前…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.85,0:21:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.44,0:21:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會讓婕希卡你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.68,0:21:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要衝動 婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MIX
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.64,0:21:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MIX
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MIX
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.59,0:21:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無限拳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有翅膀的孩子啊 我們後會有期
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.40,0:22:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…她代替我被…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.78,0:22:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MIX
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MIX
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.75,0:22:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MIX!!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============ED==========
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.61,0:22:59.38,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}君へ続く坂道に 白い花が咲いてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:07.19,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}夢から覚めたあとも 悲しい空見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.68,0:23:17.17,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}この気持ち葉っぱの裏に住んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.03,0:23:26.67,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}朝露が落ちる音に 耳をすませてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.86,0:23:34.53,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}神様 あなたが造った世界は 完璧じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.74,0:23:42.12,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}ここでは毎日恋がポロポロ 死んでゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.32,0:23:46.31,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}はじめて好きになったの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.46,0:23:49.47,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}あなたは知らないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.60,0:23:54.00,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}地球の裏側でいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.18,0:23:57.21,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}そばにいてほしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.40,0:24:01.54,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}私を忘れてもいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.76,0:24:08.05,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}そばにいてほしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.61,0:22:59.38,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}延伸到你身旁的坡道 點綴著雪白的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:07.19,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}從睡夢中驚醒之後 遠望著憂傷的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.68,0:23:17.17,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}這份青澀的感覺 依存在綠葉錯綜的紋路之間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.03,0:23:26.67,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}側耳聆聽 晨露緩緩落下的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.86,0:23:34.53,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}神明您所創造的這個世界並不完美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.74,0:23:42.12,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}因為這裡每天都有戀情一段接一段地告終
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.32,0:23:46.31,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我是初嘗戀愛的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.46,0:23:49.47,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}這個你應該不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.60,0:23:54.00,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}即便永不見天日也沒關系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.18,0:23:57.21,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我只希望你留在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.40,0:24:01.54,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}就算你把我忘卻也沒關系
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.76,0:24:08.05,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我只希望你留在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============ED==========
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.58,0:24:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很討厭膽小的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.07,0:24:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也許正因為畏懼 才能毫不猶豫的前進
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.86,0:24:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在向前邁進一步是我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.42,0:24:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 第一次重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
